addr: Tour starts at The Breakers Hotel. 1507 Ocean Ave. Spring Lake, NJ 07762
title: Candlelight Christmas Inn & House Tour
desc: Begin your Candlelight Christmas Inn & House Tour with tea and cookies at the magnificent Breakers Hotel. From there take yourself on a self-guided tour through nine properties - inns, private homes & the Historic Duggan Building - decorated in holiday splendor! Tea & cookies?being served at The Breakers from 2:00-3:00 pm. The tour is from 3:00-6:30 pm.
